latestIgtvVideos.title: Be you! Do you! Keep it you! Yes,you! 🙌🏽👊🏾
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#Artiste Don’t jump for attention. Don’t get noticed by someone. Be remembered by someone. How you smiled at them. How you made them feel. How you said a little *Thank you* with your heart. Don’t be a clown. But do the job of a clown. Make them smile like a kid. ❤️
.
.
Legit my first IGTV,Tell me what you think 💬🗯❤️ , 🎥 by @lala_photuwale , designs by @diyarajvvir and @svacouture . Publicist : @rizwanssk Courtesy : @lakmeFashionWk ✔️💯
.
.
Please tag the most sharp/dignified person you know. Fashionable is not my favourite word because people confuse being fashionable with being luxurious. It’s just a form of dignity for me, a form of art, a form of self expression. My top bet is 1️⃣ My father for his sheer innocence in terms of clothes,that is what makes him effortlessly stylish. 2️⃣ Johnny Depp because he is a walking and breathing form of self expression that doesn’t scream for anyone’s approval. 3️⃣ Saif Ali Khan for being one of the only few Indian men who exudes pure sharpness. 4️⃣ Dakku. For his gangsta swag. Yes,that. He forced me to add his name. Just saying,man! He checks my instagram.
.
.
